This is not sufficient. forkJoin-ing these requests verbatim will cause everything to be wasted if any of the API calls are errored. Reference: https://medium.com/better-programming/rxjs-error-handling-with-forkjoin-3d4027df70fc
See this, particularly on the functions passed to pipe:



